## Global Commands Reference

```bash
# Snapshots
dbt snapshot
dbt snapshot --select snapshot_name

# Packages
dbt deps                              # install packages

# Hooks verification
select * from dbt_db.raw.dbt_run_log order by run_at desc;

# Tests
dbt test --no-partial-parse
dbt test --no-partial-parse --select model_name
dbt test --no-partial-parse --store-failures
dbt test --no-partial-parse --select assert_test_name

# Compile to check generated SQL
dbt compile --no-partial-parse --select model_name
```

