## Test Types — Full Reference

| Type | Location | Reusable | yml needed | Use for |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| Built-in | dbt core |  | schema.yml | unique, not_null, accepted_values, relationships |
| dbt_expectations | packages |  | schema.yml | Advanced checks — regex, range, threshold |
| Custom generic | `macros/` |  | schema.yml | Your own reusable rules |
| Singular | `tests/` |  | None | Cross-layer business rules |

